data.description: Beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located just off Woodruff Road, offering convenience to shopping and restaurants. This inviting residence boasts a rocking chair front porch, a 2-story foyer, and dining room leading into an open concept living area with a fireplace. The updated kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and upgraded fixtures. All bedrooms and laundry are conveniently situated on the second floor, with a spacious primary suite offering a trey ceiling, dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower, and a generous walk-in closet. Enjoy the ample fenced-in corner lot with an irrigation system, perfect for outdoor activities. Neighborhood amenities include a pool and playground.  Mauldin City provides trash service and yard debris pick-up.  Zoned for Mauldin school district.
